          "slidecontent": "• Limit which machines and systems can talk to each other across your network\n• Segment your OT and IT environments\n• Apply strict access controls to any AI tools handling production data\n• Regularly audit what data your AI systems collect, store, and share\n• Keep AI software and connected devices patched and up to date\n• Train staff to spot unusual system behaviour early"
